You're doing this, say yourself or with your team,

39
00:02:16.658 --> 00:02:20.726
and you're looking at the different assignments and resources that you have,

40
00:02:20.726 --> 00:02:25.011
and you're laying out the schedule, not that complicated really.

41
00:02:25.011 --> 00:02:27.875
Then at the very bottom in the lower right,

42
00:02:27.875 --> 00:02:32.011
I have the start date and the end date for the entire project.

43
